{"word":"ἀπάτωρ","slug":"ἀπάτωρ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀπάτωρ</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:πατήρ'><el>πατήρ</el></a>\n<p/><i>without father, fatherless</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>: <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <el>ἀπ. ἐμοῦ</el> <i>not having</i> me <i>for a father</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/>"}]}